{"tid":1545103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇大陸微博發現左D野","createTime":"2019-09-05T20:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T20:35:44.000Z","uid":307156,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3d10080b72a7d2b0240e2c0b02fa90bfe73cd3","tid":1545103,"uid":307156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:03:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/6011391162/I5zOYf485?refer_flag=1001030103_&amp;type=comment#_rnd1567712415027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2F6011391162%2FI5zOYf485%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%26type%3Dcomment%23_rnd1567712415027&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=4aa15ac4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/6011391162/I5zOYf485?refer_flag=1001030103_&amp;type=comment#_rnd1567712415027</a><br />\nE條片係831太子站畜龍小隊亂打人既片,入面D人都係話打得好,大快人心<br />\n但係我見到其他留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqU1VYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqU1VYP.png&h=2f0daa10&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVQ1bw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVQ1bw9.png&h=e118f5d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3r0MnDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3r0MnDQ.png&h=f915e31a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sPgS2DQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsPgS2DQ.png&h=7cc5d0dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nD人好似E家先知D黑警係咁樣打人,仲話早就應該咁<br />\n但係其實早就已經係咁,點解最近先放E D片出泥<br />\n明明E D係唔見得光既野,有腦都會覺得D黑警傻撚左<br />\n比佢地打到就自動變成暴徒廢青港獨<br />\n放E D片到底有無咩目的呢,中共唔係應該開始淆個人權法咩<br />\n仲有E條大陸KOL曝料一哥一睇就知係幫中共文宣係咁放D香港既片"},{"pid":"d88b2a928befc1e58becd10d806a7895ff885129","tid":1545103,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-li